perl-font-ttf|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
perl-font-ttf: perl-font-ttf (Perl library for modifying TTF font files)
perl-font-ttf:
perl-font-ttf: Perl module for TrueType font hacking. Supports reading, processing
perl-font-ttf: and writing of the following tables: GDEF, GPOS, GSUB, LTSH, OS/2,
perl-font-ttf: PCLT, bsln, cmap, cvt, fdsc, feat, fpgm, glyf, hdmx, head, hhea, hmtx,
perl-font-ttf: kern, loca, maxp, mort, name, post, prep, prop, vhea, vmtx and the
perl-font-ttf: reading and writing of all other table types.
perl-font-ttf:
perl-font-ttf: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Font-TTF/
perl-font-ttf:
perl-font-ttf: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
